```plantuml
@startuml staples-sparx_Wonko

actor User
participant "wonko-client" as WonkoClient
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "src/wonko/kafka/consume.clj" as KafkaConsumer
participant "src/wonko/alert.clj" as AlertProcessor
participant "PagerDuty" as PagerDuty
participant "src/wonko/export/prometheus.clj" as PrometheusExporter
participant "Prometheus" as Prometheus

User -> WonkoClient: Submit metric/event
WonkoClient -> Kafka: Publish event
Kafka -> KafkaConsumer: Consume event
KafkaConsumer -> AlertProcessor: Process event
alt Alert condition met
    AlertProcessor -> PagerDuty: Trigger alert
end
AlertProcessor -> PrometheusExporter: Generate Prometheus metric
PrometheusExporter -> Prometheus: Expose metrics

@enduml
```